post_text: MONDAY MOTIVATION: It's August, and we're excited to meet our scholars! Whether you've chosen our traditional, virtual, or hybrid model, here are four tips to help motivate scholars as they transition back to school: (1) Ease back into a school based sleep schedule. (2) Visit our school virtually or in person. (3) Stay positive about any stress or anxiety your children may be expressing. (4) Be open about safety and hygiene. #WeareCLPA #theCLPAdifference #enrichedacademics #enrolltoday

Horizon Education Centers
January 29 at 4:31 PM ·

Old Brooklyn Horizon 1st Annual Kindergarten Fair Family Night was a big hit!!
Schools provided kindergarten readiness activities, parents learned how to enroll their child for kindergarten, learned about different schools and which school would meet the needs of their child. Every family went home with new books to enjoy and goodies from all the school sponsors. Cleveland State University provided families with information on how to continue their education.
Thank you to all the schools and organizations for being a part of this. #oldbrooklyn #upk #preschool #kindergartenreadiness
